          "slidecontent": "• Always review AI-generated content for unintended bias before including it in your script\n• Check for originality\n• AI can replicate familiar story patterns, so push beyond its first suggestions to find your unique voice\n• Keep the narrative decisions yours, using AI as a tool rather than the author\n• Watch for factual errors, cultural insensitivities, and stereotypes that AI may introduce without warning\n• As a next step, try rewriting one AI-generated scene entirely in your own words to strengthen your creative ownership"
